(9040, 'ergotamine tartrate and caffeine', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Ergotamine tartrate and caffeine should not be administered with other vasoconstrictors. The beta-blocker Inderal (propranolol) has been reported to potentiate the vasoconstrictive action of ergotamine tartrate and caffeine by blocking the vasodilating property of epinephrine.', 'DailyMed'),
