(1019, 'enasidenib mesylate', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Consider reducing the frequency of caffeine intake from various food and beverages in a 24 hour period while taking IDHIFA because IDHIFA may increase the effect of caffeine in patients who are sensitive to it.', 'DailyMed');
